donutchart.name: donut
donutchart.description:
The donut-chart shows samples as rims and categories as slices on those rims.

You can choose to enable / disable log scaling and select the sample label by metadata field.

Click a category to drill down to the next level. The layout tab has options to adjust the general layout of the donut-chart.
